\c 15
\s Sauro anokunda Amareki
\p
\v 1 Zvino Samueri wakati kuna Sauro: Jehovha wakatuma ini kuti ndikuzodze kuva mambo pamusoro pevanhu vake, pamusoro paIsraeri; naizvozvo ikozvino teerera kuinzwi remashoko aJehovha\x + 9.16.\x*.
\p
\v 2 Anoreva seizvi Jehovha wehondo: Ndichacherekedza izvo zvakaita Amareki kuna Israeri\x + 27.8. 28.18. 30.1. Eki. 17.8,14,16. Num.. 14.45. 24.20. Det. 25.17-19. 2 Sam. 8.12. 1 Makor. 4.43. Map. 83.7. Vato. 3.13.\x*, kuti wakamira sei kumurwisa naye panzira paakakwira kubva kuEgipita\x + 1 Madz. 20.12.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino enda unorova Amareki, ugoparadza kwazvo zvose zvaanazvo, usamurega\x + Rev. 27.28,29. Josh. 6.17,21.\x*; asi uraya kubva kumurume kusvika kumukadzi, kubva kumucheche kusvika kune anoyamwa, kubva kumombe kusvika kugwai, kubva kukamera kusvika kumbongoro\x + 22.19.\x*.
\p
\v 4 Zvino Sauro wakadana vanhu\x + 23.8.\x*, ndokuvaverenga paTeraimi, zvuru mazana maviri zvevaifamba netsoka, uye varume zvuru gumi vekwaJudha\x + Josh. 15.24.\x*.
\v 5 Sauro ndokusvika paguta raAmareki, ndokuvandira pamupata.
\v 6 Sauro ndokuti kuVaKeni\x + 27.10. Vato. 1.16.\x*: Endai mubve, burukai kubva pakati peVaAmareki, zvimwe ndikubvisei pamwe navo; nokuti imwi makaita tsitsi nevana vose vaIsraeri pakukwira kwavo kubuda muEgipita\x + Eki. 18.10,19. Num.. 10.29,32.\x*. Naizvozvo vaKeni vakabva vakabuda pakati paAmareki.
\v 7 Zvino Sauro wakarova Amareki\x + 14.48.\x* kubva paHavhira\x + Gen.. 2.11.\x* \add kusvika\add* wasvika paShuri riri pamberi peEgipita\x + 27.8. Gen.. 16.7.\x*.
\v 8 Zvino wakabata Agagi mambo weVaAmareki ari mupenyu, uye vanhu vose wakavaparadza kwazvo nekwakapinza kwemunondo\x + 27.8. 30.1.\x*.
\v 9 Asi Sauro nevanhu vakarega Agagi, nezvakanakisisa zvemakwai, nezvemombe, nezvezvakakora, nemakwayana, nezvose zvakanaka, uye havana kuda kuzviparadza zvachose; asi chinhu chose chinozvidzika nechakaonda, icho vakaparadza zvachose\x + 15.3,15. 28.18.\x*.
\p
\v 10 Zvino shoko raJehovha rakasvika kuna Samueri, richiti:
\v 11 Ndinozvidemba kuti ndakaisa Sauro ave mambo, nokuti wadzoka kubva pakunditevera, uye haana kusimbisa mashoko angu. Zvino zvakarwadza Samueri, iye ndokuchema kuna Jehovha usiku hwose.
\v 12 Zvino Samueri wakamuka mangwanani-ngwanani kunochingamidza Sauro. Zvino zvakaudzwa Samueri zvichinzi: Sauro wakasvika paKarimeri, tarira wakazvimisira shongwe, zvino wakatenderera, wapfuura, waburukira kuGirigari.
\v 13 Zvino Samueri wakasvika kuna Sauro, Sauro ndokuti kwaari: Uropafadzwe iwe naJehovha; ndasimbisa shoko raJehovha.
\v 14 Samueri ndokuti: Kuchema uku kwemakwai zvino chii munzeve dzangu, nekukuma kwemombe kwandinonzwa?
\v 15 Sauro ndokuti: Vauya nazvo kubva kuVaAmareki, nokuti vanhu vakarega zvakanakisisa zvemakwai nezvenzombe, kuti vabaire Jehovha Mwari wenyu; asi zvakasara takaparadza zvachose.
\v 16 Samueri ndokuti kuna Sauro: Rega, zvino ndichakuzivisa izvi Jehovha zvaataura kwandiri usiku hwuno. Iye ndokuti kwaari: Taurai.
\v 17 Samueri ndokuti: Handiti, pawaiva mudiki pameso ako, wakava musoro wemarudzi aIsraeri? Uye Jehovha wakakuzodza kuva mambo pamusoro paIsraeri.
\v 18 Jehovha ndokukutuma parwendo, ndokuti: Enda, ugonoparadza chose vatadzi, muAmareki, urwe navo kusvika ivo vapera\x + 9.21.\x*.
\v 19 Zvino sei usina kuteerera kuinzwi raJehovha, ndokubhururukira kuzvakapambiwa, ndokuita chakaipa pameso aJehovha\x + 14.32.\x*?
\p
\v 20 Sauro ndokuti kuna Samueri: Zvirokwazvo ndakateerera inzwi raJehovha, uye ndakaenda nenzira Jehovha yaakandituma, uye ndakauya naAgagi mambo waAmareki, uye ndakaparadza VaAmareki\x + 15.13.\x* zvachose.
\v 21 Asi vanhu vakatora pane zvakapambiwa, makwai nenzombe\x + 15.15.\x*, zvakanaka pane zvai\add fanira ku\add*paradzwa zvachose, kuti vabaire kuna Jehovha Mwari wenyu paGirigari\x + Rev. 27.28,29. Josh. 6.17,21.\x*.
\v 22 Samueri ndokuti: Ko Jehovha angafarira zvipo zvinopiswa nezvibairo, se\add zvaanoita\add* pakuteerera inzwi raJehovha here\x + Map. 40.6-8. 50.8,9. Zvir. 21.3. Isa. 1.11-17. Jer. 7.22,23. VaHeb. 10.6-9.\x*? Tarira, kuteerera kuri nani pane chibairo; kunzwa pane mafuta emakondohwe\x + Mup. 5.1. Hos. 6.6. Mat. 9.13. 12.7. Mik. 6.6-8. Mako 12.33.\x*.
\v 23 Nokuti upanduki \add hwakafanana\add* \add ne\add*chivi cheuroyi, uye kusindimara \add ne\add*chakaipa neterafimi\x + Gen.. 31.19.\x*. Nokuti wakaramba shoko raJehovha, iyewo wakakuramba pakuva mambo\x + 13.14.\x*.
\p
\v 24 Zvino Sauro wakati kuna Samueri: Ndakatadza, nokuti ndakadarika murairo waJehovha nemashoko enyu\x + 26.21.\x*, nokuti ndakatya vanhu, ndikateererawo kuinzwi ravo\x + 12.14. Zvir. 29.25.\x*.
\v 25 Naizvozvo zvino, kanganwirai henyu chivi changu, mugodzoka neni, kuti ndinamate Jehovha.
\v 26 Samueri ndokuti kuna Sauro: Handidzoki newe, nokuti wakaramba shoko raJehovha, naJehovha wakuramba pakuva mambo pamusoro paIsraeri\x + 15.23. 16.1.\x*.
\v 27 Samueri wakati achitendeuka kuti aende, iye ndokubata mupendero wenguvo yake, iyo ndokubvaruka\x + 1 Madz. 11.30,31.\x*.
\v 28 Samueri ndokuti kwaari: Jehovha wabvarura umambo hwaIsraeri kubva kwauri nhasi, ndokuhupa umwe wekwako ari nani panewe\x + 28.17,18.\x*.
\v 29 Uyewo Simba raIsraeri haritauri nhema kana kuzvidemba; nokuti haasi munhu kuti azvidembe\x + Num.. 23.19.\x*.
\v 30 Zvino akati: Ndakatadza, ndikudzei henyu ikozvino pamberi pevakuru vevanhu vangu nepamberi paIsraeri, mudzoke neni, kuti ndinamate Jehovha Mwari wenyu.
\v 31 Naizvozvo Samueri wakadzoka kutevera Sauro; Sauro ndokunamata kuna Jehovha\x + 15.25.\x*.
\p
\v 32 Zvino Samueri wakati: Swededzai kwandiri Agagi mambo waAmareki. Agagi ndokuenda kwaari akafara. Agagi ndokuti: Zvirokwazvo kuvava kwerufu kwabva.
\v 33 Samueri ndokuti: Munondo wako sezvawakashaisa vakadzi vana, saizvozvo mai vako vachashaiwa vana pakati pevakadzi\x + Vato. 1.7.\x*. Samueri ndokuguranya Agagi pamberi paJehovha\x + Vato. 8.21.\x* paGirigari\x + 15.12,21.\x*.
\p
\v 34 Zvino Samueri wakaenda kuRama\x + 1.19.\x*; naSauro wakakwira kumba kwake kuGibhiya raSauro\x + Josh. 18.28.\x*.
\v 35 Zvino Samueri haana kuzouyazve kuona Sauro kusvika pazuva rekufa kwake\x + 19.24.\x*; asi Samueri wakachemera Sauro\x + 16.1.\x*; naJehovha wakazvidemba kuti waiva aisa Sauro ave mambo pamusoro paIsraeri\x + 15.11.\x*.
